# Review Command

When the user's message is "review" (or "review my vault", "run review", "how's my vault", etc.):

1. Count notes in each folder (Daily Notes, Quick Capture, Personal, Work, Archive)
2. List any notes in Quick Capture (need organizing)
3. Read all daily notes and list open tasks (`- [ ]`) grouped by Personal and Work
4. Read all standalone task notes (tagged `task`, `done: false`) and list them
5. Flag any quick tasks that are overdue
6. Flag any working tasks not modified in 14+ days

Output format:

```
Daily Notes:    X notes
Quick Capture:  X notes (need organizing)
Personal:       X notes
Work:           X notes
Archive:        X notes

Open Tasks — Personal:
  - [ ] task from [[daily note or task note]]

Open Tasks — Work:
  - [ ] task from [[daily note or task note]]

Overdue / Stale:
  - task details

Needs attention:
  - anything else
```
